signs a status to a student based on their grade.

● Pass: Grade is greater than or equal to 50.

● Fail: Grade is less than 50.

● Distinction: 

Grade is greater than or equal to 80.

% Facts:/

student_grade(Student, Grade).

student_grade(alice, 90).

student_grade(bob, 45).

student_grade(charlie, 60).

student_grade(david, 85).

% Rules passed(Student) :- 

student_grade(Student, Grade),

Grade >= 50.

failed(Student) :- 

student_grade(Student, Grade),

Grade < 50.

 distinction(Student) :-
 
student_grade(Student, Grade),

Grade >= 80.
